title: Oppai no Oppai ni Yoru Oppai no Tame no Oppai
description:
A book with separate unrelated chapters, each one is drawn by a different artist.
The main theme is oppai.

Artists: 
Ch01: Kichi8 (きちはち)
Ch02: Kosuke Haruhito (虎助遥人)
Ch03: Takeyuu (タケユウ)
Ch04: Deyuyama (でゆ山)
Ch05: Imachi (いまち)
Ch06: Suzuki Nago (鈴木和)
Ch07: Detchi (でっち)

Release: 2014-10-31
Chapters: 7
Pages: 164
